description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you enjoy outdoor activities and value a good work life balance with access to outstanding beaches for swimming, surfing and kite surfing or walking along coastal paths surrounded by Exmoor and Dartmoor national parks then join us at North Devon District Hospital.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about Patient Care? We are looking for qualified nurses to join our Bank. We want nursing staff that are enthusiastic, committed and prepared to go that extra mile for our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting dedicated and motivated individuals to join the Theatre Nurse Bank at North Devon District Hospital based in Barnstaple.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer flexible working, an attractive salary, development opportunities and much, much more. If this appeals to you we welcome your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are currently employed by the Trust and want to join the Northern Healthcare Trust Staff Bank then please contact the recruitment team at ndht.staffbank@nhs.net as you do not need to apply for this vacancy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews will be completed via Zoom or telephone during the current climate.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
